Transmute vendors third-party runtime components under `vendor/` for local browser-side
format handling and encoding.

Current vendored components:
- `vendor/avif`: AVIF encoder runtime used for local AVIF output
- `vendor/elheif`: HEIC and HEIF codec runtime used for local HEIC and HEIF output
- `vendor/ktx-parse`: KTX and KTX2 container parsing helpers
- `vendor/magick`: ImageMagick WebAssembly runtime used for broad image read and write support
- `vendor/upng`: APNG encoding helpers and bundled DEFLATE support

These components remain subject to their upstream licences and notices.
